xmp

Enum NameSpace

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<NameSpace>
      • xmp.NameSpace
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<NameSpace>

    public enum NameSpace
extends java.lang.Enum<NameSpace>
    Defines the standard XMP namespaces used to qualify properties within an XMP metadata packet. Each constant encapsulates a preferred prefix and its corresponding absolute URI as defined by the XMP Specification and the ISO 16684-1 standard.
    Since:
    25 September 2025
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Trevor Maggs
